<body>
Bottom bar contain a few useful options.<br> Items, which don't fit on the screen will be available in popup window by click on <strong>More</strong> item. <br>
<br>
Holding <strong>Alt</strong> option you will enable <strong>multi select</strong> mode, i.e. click on file will select it, not open.
<br>
<strong>Select</strong> action is used to select files on active panels using string pattern.<br>
<strong>Menu</strong> option opens context menu with file actions.<br>
<strong>New</strong> option is used to create new file/folder in currently active panel<br>
<strong>Help</strong> opens help window<br>
<strong>Settings</strong> opens settings window<br>
<strong>Quick view</strong> replace inactive panel to show some information about active panel<br>
<strong>Diff</strong> option is used to show difference between currently selected directories (in active and inactive panels). Different files will be selected after operation will be performed.<br>
<strong>Find</strong> option is used to find files. Different search options are supported.<br>
